# Usa, Republic of Bashkortostan

}}
Usa (; , Uśı) is a rural locality (a village) in Ilyino-Polyansky Selsoviet, Blagoveshchensky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 11 as of 2010. There is 1 street.
Geography
Usa is located 34 km east of Blagoveshchensk (the district's administrative centre) by road. Sokolovskoye is the nearest rural locality.
